channel.title: Need some help here
channel.description: I need help. Whenever I start moparscape 3.0 it starts to download the cache but then it says connection error retry in...and stays that way. Is there any way to download the cache and add it to the moparscape folder or use the old moparscape cache? I just found out the the cache saves to C:/windows/.mpr_file_store_32/ so could someone compress everything in that folder and put a download link for it? :(
